title: Merge pull request #1 from PatrickDattilio/master
message:
Merge pull request #1 from PatrickDattilio/master

Added OnWordHighlightedListener.

This listener gives us a listener AFTER a word has been selected and determined valid. With this we can clear the board using this listener and avoid the race condition that causes the last selected item to remain selected.

title: Refactoring code to better use BoardPoint and BoardView.
message:
Refactoring code to better use BoardPoint and BoardView.

We don't need to check every position of the int[] array to check if two BoardWord instances are equal. Simply checking if they have the same string, start point and direction suffices.
